      "value": "<p><strong>Level 1</strong> Evocation</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 reaction</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 60 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p>\n\nThe creature that damaged you is momentarily surrounded by green flames. It makes a Dexterity saving throw, taking 2d10 Fire damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The damage increases by 2d10|1-9|1d10 for each spell slot level above 1.</p>",
